Thanks ahead of time when(if) this gets 20k views to everyone who clicked the link :D although now when i look back at this server, it's complete useless shit, but back then, it was the shit :D once again, thank you, even if you didn't post.
FOR A BETTER SERVER, GET THE UPDATED VERSION HERE: http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,410315.0.html
no damn fudgeing pictures again... (i didn't write fudgeing wth lolz)
i'd make a vid and put it on youtube if i still had this on my computer and had my highspeed working ;s
WOOOT 10k VIEWS!@!@!
NEEDING PEOPLE TO HELP HERE- post if theres a broken link -pl0x with cookie flavoured waffles on top :3
Ok, i need everyone who downloaded this with fast internet to upload the client and give me the links so i can help people, big help thanx, Mike
BLAH, well it seems i made an error and uploaded the wrong server files WITH the pvp drops working in the server, they are there, just not called in the client.java I took the time to re add it, upload and release again, so if you previously download the SERVER files, Redownload JUST THE SERVER FILES.
=====================SMALL TUTORIAL ON CHANGING THE CLIENT BACKROUND== Ok for all you people who hate the backround because it's hard to read Simply download another client with the backround you like Now open two screens showing both client files And on both open "sprites" folder (if the client u downloaded doesnt have it, download Pkjadscape client) then open the pictures on my client to see what they are, the titles are self explanitory now when you find the ones you don't like open the other client find the exact same title open it and click "save as" now place it in prodigyscape sprites folder with the exact same Name/Title and it will overwrite it.
Compile and reload your client and it should have changed. THIS IS FOR THE BACKROUNDS USING THE THINGS SUCH AS INVENTORY/CHAT BACKROUND and this is also a side note, DO NOT change ANY title/names of pictures or it will not load your client properly unless you change it through the coding as well. for example ClientDp (client backround when you log in) do the same thing as above to get the new picture and DONT change the name 100% at all.
================END OF TUTORIAL================================
Everything below is copy and pasted from my development page, i gave up on this and am working on a new project i hope you enjoy, flame if you want idc.
this isn't 100% complete i deleted all character files as well, i took out my ip for my server in the client, and idk what else to say, if you like, comment if not, comment, i want to here what you have to say so i can try to improve(im asking for contructive critism, not "THIS SERVER SUCKS")
if you need help with anything, pm me and ill try to answer
also - this server and client was used with jdk6 update 12, if you have a higher or lower, you will need to change it so u can "compile" you server and or "run" your server.
to make yourself admin - log in with an account (if you can't log in for any reason, just run your server, and for the "server ip" leave it blank or type 127.0.1.1 and try logging in), then log out. Go to your server files > characters, select your name, and where you see "character -playerrights = 0, change the 0 to what you want, 1-mod- 2admin - 3 owner.
have fun, hope you all enjoy it i tried to my best ability to make as much of moparscapes EPIC model forums and their tutorials for how to get rs models :)
credits to all u noobs that bished me out xD and this source i say again ISNT PWNSCAPE IDK WHERE THE HELL YOU COME UP WITH THAT. i stated and also will re-state, i used pkjad scape.
and for all you noobs, i called my pk system methods using "waffle1" "waffle2" etc, simply go to the item.java file, where u set where the item wields etc, and search "waffle" and there should be ALOT of "391" and etc, which is basically food and in there are some drops, the more food ids u add, it makes the other ids entered less common. i believe 1 is just food another is nub items like pots the other is decent ish items like rune the next is barrows items and the last is d claws, and pvp armour ETC
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Server UPDATED- http://www.mediafire.com/?wnynjdzvmmj http://uppit.com/v/3MTSRYLK - mirror2 Client- http://www.mediafire.com/?2ytxmwzj0mt - http://www.mediafire.com/?wjvm0tmgjou - updated http://uppit.com/v/72N3A0UT - newest one
OTHER PEOPLES LINKS- Client download: http://www.mediafire.com/download.php?ztzjzm2zy0w
Server download: http://www.mediafire.com/download.php?2bmm1vxigud
no other mirrors sorry, if link doesn't work, pm me and ill re upload to somewhere else.
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- //This Is My First 317 server\\ Base= Delta! :), and then based off pkjadscape (thx i give tons of creds to u for quests :)) Customs:
All customs work 100% Dplate= exact rs copy dclaws working spec all custom weapons(mayb 70% i mean) have specs, like statius vesta dual sgs ss etc
Pvp drop system- YEE took for ever to get this right, made one small mistake which madee it hard basic set up, when player kill player, the player will drop 20 items of those 20 15 are always food, manta, shark or lobs the other 5 r either 1 pvp drop(RARE) or food 1 Barrows item(lil less rare than pvp) or food and the other 3 r basic item, rune pl8, obby cape, addy pl8, rings, ammys etc or food
this is all based off rs pvp drop system, currently working on getting a uhhh player value system added so people cant spam kill for money(fixed that by making drops very rare, and preventing multi log ins, and added a sM so if a admin or owner is on, they can see if a player is dieing consistantly, he can check it out)
current bosses added- saradomin Custom (custom boss, not actual rs sara) zammy boss real rs bandos real bandos + mini bosses arma real rs arma, + mini bosses corp beast + rev drag in king dag area(very open easy access) summonboss(steeltitan+geyser titan + pickupstixx npc) drops more charms and stuff more common kbd kq titan training dragon training
